DBsheetConfig.query: SELECT T1.Id, T1.GroupingId, T1.SpotLag, T5.value IndexName, T6.value FixedDayCounter, T1.PaymentLag, T8.value EOM, T9.value FixedFrequency, T10.value FixedConvention, T11.value FixedPaymentConvention, T12.value RuleName FROM ORE.dbo.ConventionsOIS T1 LEFT JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesIndexName T5 ON T1.IndexName = T5.value LEFT JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesDayCounter T6 ON T1.FixedDayCounter = T6.value LEFT JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesBool T8 ON T1.EOM = T8.value LEFT JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesFrequencyType T9 ON T1.FixedFrequency = T9.value LEFT JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesBusinessDayConvention T10 ON T1.FixedConvention = T10.value LEFT JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesBusinessDayConvention T11 ON T1.FixedPaymentConvention = T11.value LEFT JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesDateRule T12 ON T1.RuleName = T12.value

field.name: *IndexName
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value IndexName,!T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesIndexName !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: *FixedDayCounter
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value FixedDayCounter, !T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesDayCounter !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: EOM
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value EOM, !T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesBool !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: FixedFrequency
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value FixedFrequency, !T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesFrequencyType !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: FixedConvention
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value FixedConvention,!T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesBusinessDayConvention !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: FixedPaymentConvention
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value FixedPaymentConvention,!T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesBusinessDayConvention !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: RuleName
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value RuleName,!T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesDateRule !T! ORDER BY value
